snippet.title: They Came From a Communist Planet - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
THEY CAME FROM A COMMUNIST PLANET is a first-person riot game where aliens reach earth and trigger a socialist revolution. Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1176460/They_Came_From_a_Communist_Planet/

Trailer music by Darcy Welsh (https://www.instagram.com/darcywelshmusic/), Hugh McCarthy, and David Cribb.

Follow the game on itch.io: https://colestia.itch.io/they-came-from-a-communist-planet
Follow us on Twitter: @colestia3 and @small_signs
